Package: infra
Type: Package
Title: Project Infrastructure Setup Utility
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: person("Miguel", "Rodo", email = "miguel.rodo@uct.ac.za", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A command-line tool for setting up standard project infrastructure,
    including devcontainers, README templates, and repository lists — for both
    individual repositories and multi-repo compendia.
    Provides wrappers for Bash scripts that handle devcontainer generation,
    README and repos.list template creation, and GitHub Actions workflow setup.
